titles.title: Raising a question of the priveleges of the House.

action.text: Mr. Hoyer moved to table the measure.
On motion to table the measure Agreed to by recorded vote: 219 - 189, 13 Present (Roll no. 402).

bill.summary:
5/22/2007--Introduced.
Declares that the Member from Pennsylvania, Mr. Murtha, has been guilty of a violation of the Code of Official Conduct and merits the reprimand of the House for the same.
